4	// 32-bar arrangement is exactly the 60-second run. The core conceit — the
5	// payload crosses one accelerator ring on every beat — makes the quarter-note
6	// grid the level's unit of distance as well as time: 4 rings per bar,
7	// 112 rings from breech to muzzle, and the gun fires on the downbeat of
8	// bar 28 whether or not the player survives what happens next.
